Privacy Policy

We take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in the Elite Membership Vendor app, which is used by authorized administrators to validate user discount cards via QR scans.

Information We Collect

Admin Account Information
Pre-registered admins must log in using credentials provided by the system (email + password) stored and authenticated via our secure API server.

Session tokens may be cached locally for persistent login .

Camera access (QR scans).

Profile Pictures (if uploaded by admins).

QR Scan Data (Temporary Processing)
When scanning a user’s Elite Membership card QR code, the app sends the QR data to our API to validate, then return the following information as card details:

Cardholder’s name, photo, address, phone, job, validity status, and expiration dates.

This data is never stored on the device or app—it is processed in real-time and discarded after validation.

Device & Technical Information
IP address, timestamp, and device type (for security logging and API troubleshooting).

Device Information (Automatically Collected)
IP address and timestamp for API request logging (anonymous, for security and debugging).

How We Use Your Information
Authenticate admins via our API server.

Validate Elite Membership cards in real-time.

Improve app performance (anonymous error logs).

Data Storage & Security
Admin credentials: Stored only on our encrypted API server—never locally.

Session tokens: Stored locally for persistent login .

QR scan data: Never saved locally only transient API validation.

Profile pictures (if uploaded by admins): Stored on the api server (optional).

Third-Party Services
Our API server: Handles all authentication and card validation.

No third-party logins (Google/Facebook) or advertising networks are used.

We do not share data with advertisers or other third parties.

Data Safety
All API calls use HTTPS encryption.

Admin accounts are pre-approved; no public signups.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
This policy is effective as of April 28, 2025. Updates will be posted in-app or emailed to admins.

Contact Information
For questions about this policy or data practices, contact:
Email: info@elitessg.com